      "id": "P_COMPARE_THE_ANALOG_VOLTAGE_DIFFERENCE_DIRECTLY",
      "observable_contract": "Compare the analog voltage difference directly. Drive `vout` near `vh` when `abs(V(vin1) - V(vin2)) <= match_tol`; otherwise drive it near `0 V`. The decision should be deterministic and memoryless, with a smoothed voltage transition on the output.",
